            <div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
            <div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
          </div>    <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
          <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
            <input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="email address" id="mce-EMAIL">
          </div>
            <input type="submit" value="GO" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="btn btn-info">
        </form>
      </div>
      <!--End mc_embed_signup-->
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- SCREEN 2 -->
  <div class="col-xs-12 text-center padded" id="screen2">
    <div class="screencontent-holder">
      <h2>Mangrove is a bet</h2>
      <div id="manifesto">

        <p><span class="boldmangrove">Mangrove bets that a new way of working is possible today.</span><br> A way of working that allows us to reconcile our aspiration for individual freedom and the strength of a collective united by common values. Work should not be a sacrifice or alienation, but a mean for fulfillment.</p>

        <p><span class="boldmangrove">Mangrove bets on transparency.</span><br> Transparency breeds trust and trust is the foundation of our collaboration. Rather than internal competition, we prefer the exchange of knowledge with constant goodwill. This is the source of personal enrichment and collective progress. Transparency makes us more agile and strengthens our community.</p>

        <p><span class="boldmangrove">Mangrove bets on an organization without hierarchy.</span><br> Everyone works at their own pace, the way they want and wherever they feel best. Our community thrives on the diversity of individual abilities and talents which are able to unfold within it. Such freedom goes hand in hand with our individual responsibility: our work is a commitment to the community and the rest of society.</p>

        <p><span class="boldmangrove">Mangrove bets on technology as the main organizational lever.</span><br> Scalable technology combined with our values ​​is our strength. It allows us to work horizontally in a structured way, to be more effective together while remaining free in our action.</p>

        <p><span class="boldmangrove">Mangrove is an organic and agile structure.</span><br> Mangrove is an ecosystem permeable to its environment with deep roots: we keep evolving but our principles are immutable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SCREEN 3 -->
  <div class="col-xs-12 text-center padded" id="screen3">
    <div class="responsive-holder">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Love what you just read?</h2>
      <h3>Join us in celebrating the launch of Mangrove</h3>
      <div class="row" id="event">
          <div id="eventimg">
            <%= image_tag "event1.png", id: "eventimg" %>
          </div>
